description:
Anna is barely able to contain themselves with laughter thanks to guests T.J. & his wife k8. Listen as T.J. Miller, (the reigning Critics Choice Award winner for his role as Erlich Bachman on HBO’s hit show Silicon Valley) & his wife/muse k8 (artist RosePetalPistol), open up about their relationship, and share crazy stories along the way. Anna, T.J. and k8 also give callers hilarious—and definitely unqualified—advice about public sex, dating musicians, and holding on to grudges. There’s a reason why T.J. Miller is widely considered one of the great comedic minds of this generation and we are the company he keeps.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
